description: The single source of truth for every piece of equipment, software licence, and vendor relationship the company owns — with assigned owners, renewal dates, costs, and compliance status maintained automatically. Keep your finance system and IdP. Replace the Airtable spreadsheet nobody trusts and the asset-tracking tab that's always six months out of date.
